author: Google
description:
The Doodle for Google student art contest is BACK 🔥 And this year, NBA All-Star and philanthropist Giannis Antetokounmpo is one of the judges.

U.S. K-12 students are invited to submit their art for a chance to win a college scholarship, tech package for their school, and have their art featured on google.com.

Learn More → https://doodles.google.com/d4g/

Find helpful videos to break things down into simple steps → https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLNavvvFzgaqjvbSlzzR5Jw7kwwoW53J0a&si=Xmlej4WmqGgxONEc
